---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="South Portland Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Complete guide to opening a cannabis dispensary in South Portland, Maine. Capitalize on the Portland metro market with detailed zoning and licensing information."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>South Portland Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in South Portland, Maine</p>
    </div>

    <section class="fact-box">
      <h2>📋 South Portland at a Glance</h2>
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>License Required</strong></td><td>Maine OCP Adult-Use Retail + Local license</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Local Fee</strong></td><td>$3,500 annually</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Local Tax</strong></td><td>2% local cannabis tax (unique!)</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>School Buffer</strong></td><td>500 ft minimum</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Commercial Rent</strong></td><td>$18-28/sq ft annually</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Current Dispensaries</strong></td><td>4-5 (growing)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why South Portland?</h2>
      <p>South Portland offers Portland metro access with slightly lower costs and less saturation. With 25,000+ residents and easy access to I-295, South Portland draws customers from throughout the greater Portland area.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="Casco Bay Opportunities" type="passion">
      South Portland offers the perfect balance of metropolitan access and community feel. By setting up shop here, you're positioning yourself at a strategic gateway to the Casco Bay region. It's a fantastic place to build lasting relationships with both locals and visitors!
    </Callout>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Data</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>25,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Portland Metro</td><td>230,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Moderate</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Access</td><td>I-295, Maine Turnpike</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local X-Factor: The 2% Local Tax</h2>
      <p><strong>What sets South Portland apart:</strong> South Portland is one of the few Maine municipalities with a dedicated local cannabis tax (2%). While this increases costs, it also funds local services and shows community acceptance of cannabis businesses.</p>
      <p><strong>Strategic Implication:</strong> Factor the 2% tax into pricing, but note that it signals strong local support for cannabis operations.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Area</th><th>Pros</th><th>Rent/Sq Ft</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Broadway</strong></td><td>Main street, high visibility</td><td>$22-28</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Waterman Drive</strong></td><td>Shopping area, national retailers</td><td>$18-24</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Main Street</strong></td><td>Historic district, local character</td><td>$20-26</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>✅ Opportunity:</strong> Portland metro at lower cost</li>
        <li><strong>⚠️ Factor:</strong> 2% local tax</li>
        <li><strong>💰 Investment:</strong> $350K-450K startup</li>
        <li><strong>📍 Strategy:</strong> Capture Portland overflow</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine OCP</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-license/">License Guide</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-real-estate/">Real Estate Guide</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Informational only.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .fact-box { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.1); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); }
  .fact-box h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .fact-box table { margin: 0; }
</style>